title: VTWO Crosses Above Key Moving Average Level - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Thursday, shares of the Vanguard Russell 2000 ETF (Symbol: VTWO) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $121.18, changing hands as high as $121.93 per share. Vanguard Russell 2000 shares are currently trading up about 2.4% on the day. The chart below shows the one year performance of VTWO shares, versus its 200 day moving average:     Looking at the chart above, VTWO's low point in its 52 week range is $101.11 per share, with $138.57 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $121.96.
